description: Change of use from defence establishment to provide a museum/education facility (D1 use class) 103 dwellings (C3 class) with associated car parking, ancillary service/accommodation, energy centre, works to landscape (including open space provision, boundary fencing and removal of trees) with improved means of access to the common, and including alterations and partial demolition of the mansion house, alterations and extension of building 7. Relocation of entrance to the walled garden and demolition of other listed buildings.
